# Government Tender Announcement

### Title

* English: Defence National Department (DND) Catering Services
* French: Ministère de la Défense nationale (MDN) - Services de restauration

### Reference Number and Amendment Number

* Reference Number: CB-74-7967193
* Amendment Number: 5

### Solicitation Number

* W6399-25-SL01

### Tender Notice Information

* Publication Date: April 17, 2024
* Tender Closing Date: May 22, 2024 2:00 PM
* Amendment Date: May 22, 2024
* Expected Contract Start Date: June 16, 2024
* Expected Contract End Date: June 28, 2024

### Tender Information

* Tender Status: Expired
* Procurement Category: SRV
* Procurement Method: Competitive - Open Bidding
* Selection Criteria: Lowest Price
* Trade Agreements: Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA), Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, and others.

### Contracting Information

* Contracting Entity: Department of National Defense
* Address: 101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A 0K2
* Contact Person: Sabrina Lafleur
* Email: SABRINA.LAFLEUR@forces.gc.ca
* Phone: (613) 998-4898
* Attachment: <https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/35842...>

### Tender Description

The Department of National Defense has a requirement for catering services at Huyck’s Bay Christian Camp in Wellington, Ontario for the dates of June 16 - 28, 2024. Contractors will be provided with access to the full kitchen on site and will have the option to serve meals in a take-away format, in addition to seated dining. 

For the lunch served on June 28, 2024, Contractors will be required to provide a BBQ style meal at the CFB Trenton.

Important Note: Tenderers must submit their proposal in accordance with the documents attached to this notice.

### Quantity and Type of Services Required

* The catering contract is estimated to last for 12 days, from June 16th, 2024 to June 28th, 2024.
* Contractors must have the ability to serve a variety of meals, including a BBQ-style
